                <tei:note target="#Lep_8">
                    <tei:p>Regardless the debatable reading in various places, the two funerary inscriptions are typically made up by the dedicatee's binomial onomastic formula (individual name + adpositive in -alo-/-ala) in the dative and the word pala</tei:p>
                </tei:note>
